name: Filandón
address: Carretera del Pardo a Fuencarral, 28049 Madrid, Spain
review:
Outstanding restaurant with a wonderful ambiance from the second you.pull in the drive.  The food , from the starters through the desserts, were all.... Our best meal in Madrid!! If you are looking for an authentic Spanish meal, this is it!

This place is outside of the Madrid city limit so you do need a car.... This is a beautiful restaurant with spectacular food. Let's start with the service - top notch. I noticed they pay very careful attention to detail. Place....
